<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lay2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lay,</orth> subst. stake, wager: <cit><quote>a dreadful l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 2, 27</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my fortunes against any l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 2.3.330" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. II, 3, 330</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I will have it no l.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.4.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 4, 159</bibl></cit>.
